## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some articles did not provide specific publication dates, which may affect the timeliness of the information. Additionally, the analysis is based on publicly available data, which may not capture all nuances of internal NHS funding decisions and their impacts. Further research could include interviews with NHS officials and stakeholders for a more comprehensive understanding.